Nigeria Police Say British National, Italian Abducted in Northern Town

-- B y   A r d o   H a z z a d
-- 
2011-05-13T17:26:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-13/nigeria-police-say-british-national-italian-abducted-in-northern-town.html
Gunmen in Nigeria abducted two
foreigners, a British national and an Italian, in the northern
town of Birnin Kebbi today, said  Hassan Ahmed , police
commissioner for Kebbi state.  “We’re making efforts to track the abductors,” he told
reporters in the town that is also the state capital.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ardo Hazzad in Bauchi at 
